  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/1985",
  "title": "change isarray to Array.isArray",
  "body": "When installing `react-instantsearch`, you get a warning like this:\r\n\r\n```\r\nwarning react-instantsearch > algoliasearch > isarray@2.0.1: Just use Array.isArray directly\r\n```\r\n\r\n[Array.isArray](https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/isArray) is supported in IE8+, so this should cover all our users normally.\r\n\r\n**What project are you opening an issue for?**\r\n- react-instantsearch\r\n\r\n**What is the version you are using? Always use the latest one before opening a bug issue.**\r\n\r\n3.2.0",
